{"parentUuid":"3e3f72b4-c8e1-4d2e-95b1-f150315ebb5d","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"progress","data":{"type":"hook_progress","hookEvent":"PostToolUse","hookName":"PostToolUse:Read","command":"callback"},"parentToolUseID":"toolu_019V93K6SzwonYaqacBumZ2u","toolUseID":"toolu_019V93K6SzwonYaqacBumZ2u","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:17:55.084Z","uuid":"04d46b53-1722-4df1-b7c7-fbc19aff0c19","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
{"parentUuid":"0e691836-dfa5-4447-8cc0-ae5bbed20f95","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019V93K6SzwonYaqacBumZ2u","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: strange_loop_wiring\n     3→description: Strange Loop Architecture v1.0 — ALL domains REAL, all layers LIVE, stigmergy marks, L7 evolution winners fixed. Complete closed loop. (2026-03-15)\n     4→type: project\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→# Strange Loop Architecture v1.0 (Wired 2026-03-15)\n     8→\n     9→The system crossed from executing instructions to maintaining itself through its own operations. Six components wired into a closed feedback loop.\n    10→\n    11→## The Loop (verified working)\n    12→\n    13→```\n    14→Agents → produce artifacts\n    15→    → QualityForge scores them (elegance + behavioral + dharmic)\n    16→    → RecognitionEngine synthesizes scores + identity + evolution + cascade history\n    17→    → Writes ~/.dharma/meta/recognition_seed.md\n    18→    → context.py L9 META reads seed into agent prompts\n    19→    → Agents produce better artifacts (loop closes)\n    20→```\n    21→\n    22→## What Was Wired\n    23→\n    24→| Connection | Module | Status |\n    25→|---|---|---|\n    26→| L7 Winners | context.py `_read_winners()` | LIVE — top forge scores + evolution winners |\n    27→| L8 Stigmergy | context.py `_read_stigmergy_signals()` | LIVE — hot marks + TCS + DGC health |\n    28→| L9 META | context.py `_read_recognition_seed()` | LIVE — recognition seed in all agent prompts |\n    29→| Sleep → Recognition | sleep_cycle.py `_semantic_sleep()` | WIRED — calls RecognitionEngine.synthesize(\"deep\") |\n    30→| Cascade → Feedback | cascade.py `feedback_ascent()` | WIRED — writes cascade_history.jsonl + emits signals |\n    31→| Signal bus singleton | signal_bus.py `SignalBus.get()` | WIRED — shared bus across all loops |\n    32→| Recognition loop | orchestrate_live.py `_run_recognition_loop()` | WIRED — 2h synthesis cycle in daemon |\n    33→| Daemon → Seed | mycelium daemon `_update_recognition_seed()` | LIVE — lightweight seed after identity check |\n    34→| Cascade → Recognition | meta_daemon.py signal source \"cascade\" | WIRED — reads cascade_history.jsonl |\n    35→| Cascade → Stigmergy | cascade.py `feedback_ascent()` → stigmergy | LIVE — writes marks to L8 context |\n    36→| L7 Evolution Winners | context.py `_read_winners()` | FIXED — handles dict-of-dimensions fitness |\n    37→\n    38→## Key Files\n    39→\n    40→| File | Role |\n    41→|---|---|\n    42→| `dharma_swarm/context.py` | L7+L8+L9 context layers (33K budget) |\n    43→| `dharma_swarm/meta_daemon.py` | RecognitionEngine (8 signal sources) |\n    44→| `dharma_swarm/cascade.py` | LoopEngine + feedback_ascent() |\n    45→| `dharma_swarm/signal_bus.py` | In-process event bus (singleton) |\n    46→| `dharma_swarm/sleep_cycle.py` | RecognitionEngine synthesis in SEMANTIC phase |\n    47→| `dharma_swarm/orchestrate_live.py` | Recognition loop (every 2h) |\n    48→| `dharma_swarm/models.py` | LoopDomain + LoopResult models |\n    49→| `~/.dharma/mycelium/daemon.py` | Daemon recognition seed writer |\n    50→| `~/.dharma/meta/recognition_seed.md` | The living seed (both daemon + engine write here) |\n    51→| `~/.dharma/meta/cascade_history.jsonl` | Cascade loop feedback trail |\n    52→\n    53→## Real Scoring (All 5 Domains LIVE — 2026-03-15)\n    54→\n    55→| Domain | Module | Scoring |\n    56→|---|---|---|\n    57→| code | cascade_domains/code.py | REAL — elegance.py (AST) + metrics.py (behavioral) + pytest |\n    58→| skill | cascade_domains/skill.py | REAL — structure + compression + behavioral + completeness + composability |\n    59→| common | cascade_domains/common.py | REAL — TelosGatekeeper (11 gates, fallback to basic) |\n    60→| product | cascade_domains/product.py | REAL — foreman (5 dims) + elegance + behavioral + completeness + test_quality |\n    61→| research | cascade_domains/research.py | REAL — claim_density + verifiability + novelty + rigor + relevance |\n    62→| meta | cascade_domains/meta.py | REAL — bounds validation + coverage scoring |\n    63→\n    64→## Agent Fitness Hook\n    65→\n    66→`agent_runner.py._emit_fitness_signal()` — every agent task completion emits `AGENT_FITNESS` signal to the bus with swabhaav_ratio, entropy, recognition_type. This closes the loop: agent output → behavioral score → signal bus → recognition seed.\n    67→\n    68→## CLI Commands\n    69→\n    70→- `dgc cascade [domain] [--seed-path PATH] [--seed-skill NAME]` — run cascade domain\n    71→- `dgc forge <path> [--batch <dir>]` — score artifacts\n    72→- `dgc loops` — show recognition seed + TCS + cascade history + daemon status\n    73→\n    74→## Scoring Data (Live)\n    75→\n    76→- `~/.dharma/stigmergy/mycelium_scoring_report.json` — 185 modules scored, mean 7.27★\n    77→- `~/.dharma/stigmergy/mycelium_skill_health.json` — 62 skills scored, mean 8.5★\n    78→- Context L7 reads scoring report into agent prompts\n    79→\n    80→## Cascade Scores (All Domains)\n    81→\n    82→| Domain | Seed | Fitness | Eigenform |\n    83→|---|---|---|---|\n    84→| code | (default) | 0.438 | YES |\n    85→| skill | (default) | 0.075 | YES |\n    86→| product | dharma_swarm/ | 0.638 | YES |\n    87→| research | R_V paper v007 | 0.707 | YES |\n    88→| meta | (default) | 0.000 | YES |\n    89→\n    90→### R_V Paper Breakdown (research domain)\n    91→- Relevance: 1.000 (all R_V keywords present)\n    92→- Rigor: 0.973 (genuine behavioral signature, low mimicry)\n    93→- Verifiability: 0.750 (23 citations, 258 specific numbers)\n    94→- Novelty: 0.600 (4 formal structures, multiple concepts)\n    95→- Claim density: 0.275 (51 claims in 6186 words)\n    96→\n    97→### Product Domain Detail\n    98→- Wired to foreman.py (5 quality dimensions: has_tests, tests_pass, error_handling, documented, edge_cases_covered)\n    99→- Also scores: elegance (AST), behavioral (metrics.py), completeness (README/tests/docs), test_quality\n   100→- SATYA gate correctly blocks projects containing credentials (e.g. jagat_kalyan with sk-ant-...)\n   101→\n   102→### Research Domain Detail\n   103→- 5 scoring dimensions: claim_density, verifiability, novelty, rigor, relevance\n   104→- Wired to semantic_digester.py (FORMAL_PATTERNS, _extract_claims) for novelty\n   105→- Wired to metrics.py for rigor (entropy, swabhaav_ratio, mimicry detection)\n   106→- Track-specific relevance keywords: rv, phoenix, contemplative\n   107→\n   108→## Test Coverage\n   109→\n   110→- 106 tests across test_cascade.py (60) + test_context.py (46)\n   111→- 32 domain implementation tests (code, skill, product, research, common, end-to-end)\n   112→- Full suite: 519 passed, 1 pre-existing failure (command_center import), 3 skipped\n   113→\n   114→## Remaining Items\n   115→\n   116→- All 5 cascade domains now have REAL scoring — no stubs remain\n   117→- context.py L7 evolution winners FIXED (now handles dict-of-dimensions fitness format)\n   118→- Full loop is CLOSED: all components wired, all scoring real, all layers live\n   119→"}]},"uuid":"1fe7c8ef-bcf3-4341-86e9-5f8e5e844b6c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:17:55.083Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"0e691836-dfa5-4447-8cc0-ae5bbed20f95","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
