{"parentUuid":"3d93ef60-69db-41e5-8d66-cdd5f84f5e0f","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"progress","data":{"type":"hook_progress","hookEvent":"PostToolUse","hookName":"PostToolUse:Read","command":"callback"},"parentToolUseID":"toolu_01M6W2xiMiyEFQkhS2icDTYD","toolUseID":"toolu_01M6W2xiMiyEFQkhS2icDTYD","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:17:59.329Z","uuid":"f7788ebe-403e-483a-a704-b6fe2ef89d46","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
{"parentUuid":"953cde12-cd8d-465b-b0f1-51bef597b3bf","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01M6W2xiMiyEFQkhS2icDTYD","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: ANVIL Benchmark System\n     3→description: Anti-Narcissism Verification & Intelligence Layer — lean 1,418-line baseline that benchmarks against dharma_swarm's 93K lines, reports to KaizenOps\n     4→type: project\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→ANVIL is the control group for dharma_swarm. 1,418 lines vs 93,154. Reports to KaizenOps workspace \"anvil\".\n     8→\n     9→**Why:** dharma_swarm's field_knowledge_base.py self-rates as \"DOMINANT\" with 6 moats and 42 hand-curated entries. Without an external baseline, this is a mirror not intelligence. ANVIL provides the scientific control.\n    10→\n    11→**How to apply:** Run `cd ~/anvil && python3 -m anvil.cli bench` before claiming dharma_swarm features \"supersede\" alternatives. Any dharma_swarm module that can't beat ANVIL's lean agent on the same task doesn't earn its lines.\n    12→\n    13→## Location & Usage\n    14→- **Repo**: `~/anvil/` (git, committed)\n    15→- **Run**: `cd ~/anvil && python3 -m anvil.cli bench [--tasks code_fix code_gen ...] [--dharma] [--model sonnet|haiku|llama]`\n    16→- **List tasks**: `python3 -m anvil.cli tasks`\n    17→- **Reports**: `~/.anvil/reports/bench_*.json`\n    18→- **KaizenOps**: `http://127.0.0.1:8765/?workspace=anvil`\n    19→\n    20→## Architecture (4 files, no framework)\n    21→- `anvil/tasks.py` — 10 benchmark tasks with setup/validate functions\n    22→- `anvil/engine.py` — LeanAgent (OpenRouter API), DharmaSwarmAgent (dgc subprocess), BenchmarkReport\n    23→- `anvil/kaizen.py` — KaizenOps event reporter\n    24→- `anvil/cli.py` — CLI entry point\n    25→\n    26→## First Results (2026-03-14)\n    27→- **9/10 PASS** (90%), avg score 0.86\n    28→- **$0.06 total cost**, 66.5s total time\n    29→- Failed: multi_step (SimpleKV TTL edge case)\n    30→- Model: Claude Sonnet 4 via OpenRouter\n    31→- dharma_swarm comparison not yet run (--dharma flag)\n    32→\n    33→## Key Insight\n    34→A raw API call + pytest validator in <3K lines achieves 90% on coding tasks. The 93K lines of dharma_swarm need to demonstrate value BEYOND what a bare API call provides.\n    35→"}]},"uuid":"df7516de-b4c6-440c-a9c5-c4346455cf82","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:17:59.329Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"953cde12-cd8d-465b-b0f1-51bef597b3bf","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
