{"parentUuid":"20d037e6-9192-4353-a29d-1895d86c27cd","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PCDttkUBH6T5QWtK4sqEkW","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"OpenAI strategy 2026 AGI roadmap Sam Altman plans\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Sam Altman AI 2026: ChatGPT6 and OpenAI Predictions\",\"url\":\"https://digitalstrategy-ai.com/2026/01/02/openai-sam-altman-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"OpenAI's Vision for 2026: Sam Altman Lays Out the Roadmap\",\"url\":\"https://www.theneuron.ai/explainer-articles/openais-vision-for-2026-sam-altman-lays-out-the-roadmap/\"},{\"title\":\"Sam Altman OpenAI Future: Hardware, Disney & AGI Timeline 2026\",\"url\":\"https://almcorp.com/blog/sam-altman-openai-future-ai-hardware-disney-partnership-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"😸 Sam Altman just laid out OpenAI's plan for 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.theneurondaily.com/p/sam-altman-just-laid-out-openai-s-plan-for-2026\"},{\"title\":\"OpenAI's Publicly Released Timeline: Strategy Completely Changed from 2026 to 2028\",\"url\":\"https://eu.36kr.com/en/p/3529519807518854\"},{\"title\":\"OpenAI roadmap revealed: AI research interns by 2026, full-blown AGI researchers by 2028 | TechRadar\",\"url\":\"https://www.techradar.com/ai-platforms-assistants/chatgpt/openai-roadmap-revealed-ai-research-interns-by-2026-full-blown-agi-researchers-by-2028\"},{\"title\":\"Sam Altman on OpenAI’s Plan to Win, AI Personalization, Infrastructure Math, and The Inevitable IPO\",\"url\":\"https://www.bigtechnology.com/p/sam-altman-on-openais-plan-to-win\"},{\"title\":\"I Spoke With Sam Altman: What OpenAI’s Future Actually Looks Like\",\"url\":\"https://www.cmswire.com/digital-experience/i-spoke-with-sam-altman-what-openais-future-actually-looks-like/\"},{\"title\":\"AGI by 2025? Sam Altman Reveals OpenAI’s Bold Timeline for Artificial Intelligence\",\"url\":\"https://firstmovers.ai/agi-2025/\"},{\"title\":\"Ten years | OpenAI\",\"url\":\"https://openai.com/index/ten-years/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding OpenAI's strategy, 2026 plans, and AGI roadmap according to Sam Altman:\n\n## 2026 Goals and AI Research\n\n2026 is projected to be the year of the \"AI Research Intern\"—a system capable of handling specific, complex research tasks with autonomy, serving as a critical stepping stone toward 2028, which Altman has marked as the target for a fully \"Automated AI Researcher.\" OpenAI hopes to develop an AI \"researcher intern\" in 2026 that can help accelerate the research team's ideas.\n\n## Model Releases\n\nA meaningful model improvement is expected in Q1 2026, though while consumers want better experiences, features, and faster responses rather than more raw intelligence, enterprises still want more reasoning capability, so the Q1 2026 model will push hard on enterprise capabilities while also improving the consumer experience in ways that go beyond raw intelligence.\n\n## AGI Roadmap\n\nOpenAI's timeline for AGI remains deliberately ambiguous, with Altman at one point claiming \"we basically have built AGI, or very close to it,\" then walking back the statement as \"a spiritual statement, not a literal one,\" predicting that achieving AGI will require \"a lot of medium-sized breakthroughs\" rather than a single major discovery.\n\n## Infrastructure Investment\n\nProject Stargate is a joint venture involving OpenAI, Oracle, SoftBank, and MGX, planning to invest up to $500 billion in AI infrastructure in the United States by 2029, beginning with an immediate $100 billion investment and building up to 20 large AI data centers.\n\n## Business Expansion\n\nOpenAI announced in January 2026 a suite of software tools for healthcare organizations and a freemium ad-supported business model for ChatGPT, aiming to expand toward 1 billion users.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"57c7f7c1-6c09-4eb5-a72f-e616231a3cf1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:12.682Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"20d037e6-9192-4353-a29d-1895d86c27cd","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
