{"parentUuid":"d70e6142-55d1-4243-9331-9b8cc7e01f8e","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01B4s7hQyGYSVLHoBFSzqBgt","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Palantir AIP ontology 2026 strategy government AI contracts\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"3 Reasons Palantir Is Unavoidable in AI Infrastructure by 2026\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/3-reasons-palantir-unavoidable-ai-193400121.html\"},{\"title\":\"AIPCon\",\"url\":\"https://www.palantir.com/aipcon/\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - Palantir (PLTR) 2026: The Rise of the Logic Layer and the Agentic AI Revolution\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/finterra-2026-3-5-palantir-pltr-2026-the-rise-of-the-logic-layer-and-the-agentic-ai-revolution\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - The AI Operating System of the West: A 2026 Deep Dive into Palantir Technologies (PLTR)\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/finterra-2026-3-2-the-ai-operating-system-of-the-west-a-2026-deep-dive-into-palantir-technologies-pltr\"},{\"title\":\"User | chroniclejournal.com - Palantir (PLTR) 2026: The Rise of the Logic Layer and the Agentic AI Revolution\",\"url\":\"http://markets.chroniclejournal.com/chroniclejournal/article/finterra-2026-3-5-palantir-pltr-2026-the-rise-of-the-logic-layer-and-the-agentic-ai-revolution\"},{\"title\":\"Palantir's AI-Driven Government and Enterprise Monopoly: A High-Conviction Play for 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.ainvest.com/news/palantir-ai-driven-government-enterprise-monopoly-high-conviction-play-2026-2601/\"},{\"title\":\"Overview • AIP • Palantir\",\"url\":\"https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/aip/overview\"},{\"title\":\"The AI Operating System of the West: A 2026 Deep Dive into Palantir Technologies (PLTR)\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/wral/article/finterra-2026-3-2-the-ai-operating-system-of-the-west-a-2026-deep-dive-into-palantir-technologies-pltr\"},{\"title\":\"The AI Operating System of 2026: How Palantir Became the Backbone of the Modern Enterprise\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/wral/article/marketminute-2026-1-1-the-ai-operating-system-of-2026-how-palantir-became-the-backbone-of-the-modern-enterprise\"},{\"title\":\"Peter Thiel & Alex Karp: Palantir's Rise in AI-Driven National Security (2026) - https://debuglies.com\",\"url\":\"https://debuglies.com/2026/01/12/peter-thiel-alex-karp-palantirs-rise-in-ai-driven-national-security-2026/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding Palantir's AIP ontology, 2026 strategy, and government AI contracts:\n\n## AIP and Ontology Technology\n\nPalantir's AIP (Artificial Intelligence Platform) uses Large Language Models (LLMs) to interact with the Palantir Ontology, which is a semantic layer that maps raw data to real-world objects and actions, ensuring AI models don't \"hallucinate\" and instead execute logic based on actual business rules. AIP's core capability lies in its ability to take \"raw\" LLMs (like OpenAI's GPT-4 or Anthropic's Claude) and ground them in a company's private data via the Palantir Ontology.\n\n## 2026 Strategy\n\nThe shift from \"Generative AI\" (creating content) to \"Agentic AI\" (executing tasks) has favored Palantir's Ontology-driven approach. Palantir has leaned into the \"Sovereign AI\" trend by signing multi-billion dollar framework deals with the UK and France.\n\n## Government AI Contracts\n\nPalantir secured over $800 million in Department of Defense (DoD) contracts in 2025 alone, with a landmark $10 billion enterprise agreement with the U.S. Army consolidating 75 existing contracts. In August 2025, the company secured a staggering $10 billion, 10-year contract with the U.S. Army that consolidated 75 disparate data and AI contracts into a single enterprise agreement.\n\nPalantir's government business was up 55% year-over-year in the last quarter, and the nature of these contracts creates a powerful driver of annual recurring revenue (ARR) because Palantir's platforms are embedded in long-term, mission-critical contracts with high renewal rates.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"40aca02d-d188-488a-8c5c-3d5d103fff62","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:12.827Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"d70e6142-55d1-4243-9331-9b8cc7e01f8e","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
