{"parentUuid":"c6963d2e-aab2-4e1b-bcf9-cde79cf98ded","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016smXNYhD6cm2XzU7j23Dza","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Google DeepMind Gemini 2026 strategy AGI research AlphaFold\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"AlphaGo at 10: How AI Innovation Is Paving the Path to AGI — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/10-years-of-alphago/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaGo completa 10 anos: de jogo de tabuleiro à AGI\",\"url\":\"https://www.techenet.com/2026/03/alphago-10-anos-impacto-agi-deepmind/\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_DeepMind\"},{\"title\":\"How AI Innovation Is Paving the Path to AGI — Google DeepMind - TechAIApp\",\"url\":\"https://www.techaiapp.com/tech/how-ai-innovation-is-paving-the-path-to-agi-google-deepmind/\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind & DOE Partner on Genesis: AI for Science — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/google-deepmind-supports-us-department-of-energy-on-genesis/\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind CEO Demis Hassabis predicts AGI may emerge within the next five years\",\"url\":\"https://www.pitchonnet.com/pitch-feature/google-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-predicts-agi-may-emerge-within-the-next-five-years-39014.html\"},{\"title\":\"Taking a responsible path to AGI — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/taking-a-responsible-path-to-agi/\"},{\"title\":\"About Google DeepMind — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/about/\"},{\"title\":\"What is DeepMind and How to Use it?\",\"url\":\"https://www.igmguru.com/blog/what-is-google-deepmind\"},{\"title\":\"What is Google Gemini? Complete History of DeepMind, Bard, Multimodal AI (2026) | Taskade Blog\",\"url\":\"https://www.taskade.com/blog/google-gemini-history\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Google DeepMind's 2026 strategy regarding AGI research and their use of Gemini and AlphaFold:\n\n## AGI Strategy and Timeline\n\nGoogle DeepMind CEO Demis Hassabis believes AGI is on the horizon, possibly within the next five years as of 2026. He notes that \"general purpose foundational model systems are becoming increasingly capable almost week by week.\"\n\n## Path to AGI Through Integration\n\nDeepMind believes the combination of Gemini's world models, AlphaGo's search and planning techniques, and specialized AI tool use will prove critical for AGI. More specifically, the next generation of AI systems will need to be able to call upon specialized tools, such as AlphaFold for determining protein structures.\n\n## Gemini's Role\n\nGemini is described as their largest and most capable model, and the latest Gemini models use techniques pioneered with AlphaGo and AlphaZero to think and reason across multiple modalities.\n\n## Recent Achievements and Applications\n\nDeepMind developed an AI co-scientist built on Gemini, designed to help scientists synthesize vast amounts of information to generate novel hypotheses and research proposals, and accelerate scientific and biomedical discoveries. DeepMind is applying AI to material science, fusion, physics, and mathematics, hoping AlphaFold will be \"the first example of amazing advances enabled by it.\"\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"a86983b5-1216-4489-94a9-619e34acf6db","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:40.315Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"c6963d2e-aab2-4e1b-bcf9-cde79cf98ded","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
