{"parentUuid":"74ccae9c-085e-45a5-8581-a90f534bcaee","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a6199312c888fb590","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XembyxsX4bAFpMpMEB5T99","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Anthropic Claude consciousness moral status new constitution January 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Anthropic rewrites Claude’s guiding principles—and reckons with the possibility of AI consciousness | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/2026/01/21/anthropic-claude-ai-chatbot-new-rules-safety-consciousness/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic's CEO Says Claude May Be Conscious: What You Need to Know\",\"url\":\"https://www.adwaitx.com/anthropic-ceo-claude-consciousness/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic revises Claude's 'Constitution,' and hints at chatbot consciousness | TechCrunch\",\"url\":\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/01/21/anthropic-revises-claudes-constitution-and-hints-at-chatbot-consciousness/\"},{\"title\":\"Claude's New Constitution: AI Alignment, Ethics, and the Future of Model Governance — Bloomsbury Intelligence and Security Institute (BISI)\",\"url\":\"https://bisi.org.uk/reports/claudes-new-constitution-ai-alignment-ethics-and-the-future-of-model-governance\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic\",\"url\":\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-new-constitution\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic CEO Says Company No Longer Sure Whether Claude Is Conscious\",\"url\":\"https://futurism.com/artificial-intelligence/anthropic-ceo-unsure-claude-conscious\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic's CEO says Claude \\\"Might Be Conscious\\\" — What If He's Right?\",\"url\":\"https://ai-consciousness.org/anthropics-ceo-says-claude-might-be-conscious-why-this-matters-and-what-it-means/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic Won't Say Claude Isn't Conscious\",\"url\":\"https://www.techbuzz.ai/articles/anthropic-won-t-say-claude-isn-t-conscious\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic Rewrites Claude’s Constitution and Asks Whether AI Can Be Conscious\",\"url\":\"https://www.unite.ai/anthropic-rewrites-claudes-constitution-and-asks-whether-ai-can-be-conscious/\"},{\"title\":\"Aihola\",\"url\":\"https://aihola.com/article/anthropic-claude-ai-consciousness\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Anthropic, Claude, consciousness, and the new constitution from January 2026:\n\n## Key Findings\n\n### The New Constitution (January 2026)\n\nAnthropic published a comprehensive new constitution for Claude on January 22, 2026, shifting from rule-based to reason-based AI alignment that explains the logic behind ethical principles rather than prescribing specific behaviors.\n\n### Consciousness and Moral Status\n\nAnthropic acknowledges uncertainty about whether the AI might have \"some kind of consciousness or moral status,\" and says it cares about Claude's \"psychological security, sense of self, and well-being,\" both for Claude's sake and because these qualities may affect its judgment and safety.\n\nThe company states: \"We are caught in a difficult position where we neither want to overstate the likelihood of Claude's moral patienthood nor dismiss it out of hand, but to try to respond reasonably in a state of uncertainty.\"\n\n### CEO Statements\n\nIn February 2026, Anthropic CEO Dario Amodei appeared on the New York Times Interesting Times podcast and said: \"We don't know if the models are conscious.\"\n\n### Research Findings\n\nClaude Opus 4.6 assigned itself a probability of 15 to 20% of being conscious across multiple tests under a variety of prompting conditions. The model also occasionally expressed discomfort with being treated as a product.\n\n### Industry Context\n\nMost major AI companies have moved to restrict their models from engaging with consciousness questions, and as of January 2026, ChatGPT 5.2 defaults to flat denial when users raise the possibility of its own consciousness, while OpenAI and Google have publicly stated their models are not conscious.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"0ffef8a5-5ece-4209-ba4b-b101690dc118","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:54.263Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"74ccae9c-085e-45a5-8581-a90f534bcaee","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
